Borrowed from {{bor|en|frm|faction}}, from {{der|en|la|factiō||a group of people acting together, a political faction}}, noun of process from perfect passive participle {{m|la|factus}}, from {{m|la|faciō||do, make}}. {{doublet|fashion|lang=en}}.

